ly avoid the use of products containing ginkgo biloba.', 'Synergism', 'Patients should consult a healthcare provider before taking any herbal or alternative medicine.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/149534/', '', 'Acetaminophen, Naloxone, Naltrexone', 'Rivastigmine, Galantamine, Donepezil, Tacrine, Memantine, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
